column3: Record ID

In this study, you will be asked to evaluate hard candies (see ingredient info below) and report your responses on a survey daily for approximately 90 days. Additionally, we will ask you to fill out a Daily COVID-19 Form to monitor any potential COVID-related symptoms. Both surveys will be completed via a mobile app called "MyCap".

We will provide you a supply of hard candies, which can be picked up Monday-Friday during business hours at three different locations near OSU campus.

If you are interested in participating, please complete the form below. A consent form, demographic survey, and instructions to download MyCap will be sent to your email in order.

If you have any questions, please email COVIDCandyTest@osu.edu with "Phase 2" on the subject line.

Candy information
Ingredients: Sugar, Simple Corn Syrup, Coconut (tree nut), Citric Acid, Natural Flavors.
Allergen: contains coconut
Calories per candy: 6 calories
